author: Lucy Sweeney And Scott Mitchell
title: If Australians don't stay home this weekend, we might face more restrictions. Here's what they could be
description: Heading into the Easter long weekend, government officials are warning Australians not to get complacent about coronavirus, or we might see restrictions scaled up. Here's what that could look like.
content:

Government officials have warned Australians not to get complacent about coronavirus just because it's Easter.
